<template>
  <el-form :ref="FormName" :model="FormData" inline>
    <template v-for="item in FormData.Info">
      <el-form-item :key="item.prop" :prop="item.prop" :label="item.label">
        <el-input
          v-if="item.type === 'input'"
          v-model="item.value"
          :type="item.prop === 'password' ? 'password' : ''"
        ></el-input>
      </el-form-item>
    </template>
  </el-form>
</template>

<script>
export default {
  name: "formFinish",
  data() {
    return {
      name: "FormName",
      FormData: {
        Info: [
          { label: "姓名", prop: "real_name", value: "cfdf", type: "input" },
          { label: "身份证号", prop: "idcard", value: "cfdf", type: "input" },
          { label: "手机号码", prop: "phone", value: "cfdf", type: "input" },
          { label: "登录账号", prop: "account", value: "cfdf", type: "input" },
          { label: "登录密码", prop: "password", value: "cfdf", type: "input" },
        ],
        Rules: {},
      },
    };
  },
};
</script>

<style></style>
